Uzalo’s Mrs Madlala has shared her story on how she ended up on Mzanzi's most watched soapie. In a video shared on the soapie’s Twitter page, actress Ntombifuthi Dlamini says she was just a cleaner at a local clinic when she was approached one afternoon to be an extra on the show. Ntombifuthi went on to say she knew nothing about acting when she was approached. WATCH VIDEO BELOW: 